Description

Write a program to reverse a 3-digit number.

Input Format

Input consists of an integer.

Output Format

The output will be the reverse of the input integers.

Sample Input

456
Sample Output

654
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------CODE------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
#include <stdio.h>
int main()
{
  int n,rem,a=0;
  scanf("%d",&n);
  while(n!=0){
    rem=n%10;
    a=a*10+rem;
    n=n/10;
  }
  printf("%d",a);
   }
